This Kanban-todo app includes the following basic functionalities:

Task creation: Users can create new tasks and assign them a title, description, and due date.
Task organization: Users can categorize tasks into different lists or tags to help with organization and prioritization.
Task editing: Users can modify existing tasks by editing the title, description, due date, or other details.
Task completion: Users can mark tasks as completed once they are finished.
Task deletion: Users can delete tasks that are no longer needed or relevant.
User account: Users can create an account to save their tasks and preferences and access them from different devices.
